  "title": "",
  "movie": "에이브의 쿠킹 다이어리 (Abe)",
  "duration_sec": 655.93,
  "audio_url": "https://pub-7f9ded590f88439d8f48752f6639e723.r2.dev/2020-09-16_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.8,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리시 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.8,
      "end": 3.74,
      "text": "9월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.74,
      "end": 6.6,
      "text": "페르난도 그로스데인 안드레이드 감독"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.6,
      "end": 7.86,
      "text": "노아 쉬납"
    },
    {
      "start": 7.86,
      "end": 9.02,
      "text": "세우 조르지"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.02,
      "end": 9.8,
      "text": "주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.8,
      "end": 12.08,
      "text": "에이베 쿠킹 다이어리"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.08,
      "end": 13.12,
      "text": "Hi Chris"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.12,
      "end": 13.98,
      "text": "Hello"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.98,
      "end": 16.2,
      "text": "Wow 저 이제 이름이 좀 익숙해졌어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.2,
      "end": 17.2,
      "text": "아 익숙해졌네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.2,
      "end": 18.58,
      "text": "좀 익숙해졌나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 18.58,
      "end": 22.58,
      "text": "네 좀 이제 편안하게 사람들의 이름을 읽을 수가 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.58,
      "end": 23.84,
      "text": "It sounded good to me"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.84,
      "end": 25.76,
      "text": "Yeah thank you so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.76,
      "end": 26.3,
      "text": "Very good"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.3,
      "end": 26.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.74,
      "end": 27.28,
      "text": "Anyway"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.28,
      "end": 29.74,
      "text": "Have you ever mediated between people"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.74,
      "end": 31.68,
      "text": "such as colleagues or your families?"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.16,
      "end": 33.3,
      "text": "Mediated fights?"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.6,
      "end": 34.97,
      "text": "Yeah sort of"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.97,
      "end": 37.55,
      "text": "Usually I was in the fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.55,
      "end": 38.85,
      "text": "when I was little"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.85,
      "end": 40.13,
      "text": "Usually oh yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.13,
      "end": 40.83,
      "text": "I was in the fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.83,
      "end": 41.21,
      "text": "Yeah yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.21,
      "end": 42.33,
      "text": "I was fighting my brothers"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.33,
      "end": 43.39,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.39,
      "end": 44.69,
      "text": "But nowadays"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.69,
      "end": 45.85,
      "text": "Recently"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.85,
      "end": 47.47,
      "text": "I try to mediate fights"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.47,
      "end": 49.19,
      "text": "It's kind of funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.19,
      "end": 49.47,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.47,
      "end": 50.59,
      "text": "Because I grew up"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.59,
      "end": 51.47,
      "text": "always fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.47,
      "end": 51.81,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.81,
      "end": 52.39,
      "text": "With my brothers"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.39,
      "end": 53.97,
      "text": "But now I'm a dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.97,
      "end": 54.27,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.27,
      "end": 54.89,
      "text": "And I have kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.89,
      "end": 56.45,
      "text": "And my two daughters"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.45,
      "end": 58.53,
      "text": "They're sweet most of the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.53,
      "end": 58.77,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.77,
      "end": 59.75,
      "text": "But they fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.75,
      "end": 60.31,
      "text": "Sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.31,
      "end": 60.75,
      "text": "Their people"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.75,
      "end": 62.57,
      "text": "You know like once a day"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.57,
      "end": 62.77,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.77,
      "end": 64.23,
      "text": "Or many many times"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.23,
      "end": 66.95,
      "text": "And I'm supposed to mediate in between them"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.95,
      "end": 67.41,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.41,
      "end": 68.57,
      "text": "And sometimes I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.57,
      "end": 70.09,
      "text": "Which side to take"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.09,
      "end": 70.35,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.35,
      "end": 71.37,
      "text": "Or who did what"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.37,
      "end": 72.95,
      "text": "Who started the fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.95,
      "end": 74.01,
      "text": "It's not easy"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.01,
      "end": 74.95,
      "text": "Ah 진짜"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.95,
      "end": 75.47,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.47,
      "end": 75.97,
      "text": "아빠"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.97,
      "end": 77.61,
      "text": "She did it"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.61,
      "end": 78.93,
      "text": "No she did it"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.93,
      "end": 79.83,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.83,
      "end": 81.23,
      "text": "It's never easy to mediate fights"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.23,
      "end": 81.63,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.63,
      "end": 83.71,
      "text": "누군가 사이에서 껴가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.71,
      "end": 85.37,
      "text": "중재자의 역할을 한다는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.37,
      "end": 87.63,
      "text": "쉽지만은 않은 일입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.63,
      "end": 88.95,
      "text": "In those cases"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.95,
      "end": 91.79,
      "text": "We have to listen to both sides carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.79,
      "end": 94.29,
      "text": "And lead them into the good sides"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.29,
      "end": 95.03,
      "text": "Always"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.03,
      "end": 95.61,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.69,
      "end": 95.99,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.99,
      "end": 97.87,
      "text": "It's even harder with adults"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.87,
      "end": 99.27,
      "text": "Like if my mother-in-law"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.27,
      "end": 101.79,
      "text": "Is fighting with my father-in-law"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.79,
      "end": 104.01,
      "text": "And I'm at the dinner table"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.01,
      "end": 106.05,
      "text": "And I like both of them"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.05,
      "end": 108.01,
      "text": "So I don't know whose side to take"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.01,
      "end": 108.67,
      "text": "어떻게"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.67,
      "end": 109.77,
      "text": "And they kind of look at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.77,
      "end": 111.09,
      "text": "Like they want me to take"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.09,
      "end": 111.97,
      "text": "Their side"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.97,
      "end": 112.15,
      "text": "편 좀 들어달라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.15,
      "end": 112.57,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.57,
      "end": 113.51,
      "text": "편 좀 들어달라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.51,
      "end": 113.81,
      "text": "네 네"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.81,
      "end": 114.47,
      "text": "막 눈빛"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.47,
      "end": 115.23,
      "text": "막 눈치를 줘요"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.23,
      "end": 115.61,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.61,
      "end": 117.53,
      "text": "So it's very 곤란하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.53,
      "end": 117.79,
      "text": "어머"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.79,
      "end": 120.29,
      "text": "우리 크리스 씨가 장인어른과"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.29,
      "end": 121.83,
      "text": "장모님 사이에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.83,
      "end": 123.55,
      "text": "어 누구 편을 들지도 못하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.55,
      "end": 124.55,
      "text": "얼마나 힘들었을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.55,
      "end": 125.33,
      "text": "생각이 듭니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.33,
      "end": 127.49,
      "text": "어린이보다 더 힘든 게 그거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.49,
      "end": 128.19,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.19,
      "end": 128.99,
      "text": "다 큰 사람들"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.99,
      "end": 129.49,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.49,
      "end": 131.55,
      "text": "그래서 그럴 때는 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.55,
      "end": 133.95,
      "text": "The word frustration fits quite well"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.95,
      "end": 135.29,
      "text": "in that kind of"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.29,
      "end": 136.11,
      "text": "Frustration?"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.23,
      "end": 136.41,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.41,
      "end": 137.93,
      "text": "It's so frustrating"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.93,
      "end": 139.29,
      "text": "So frustrating"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.29,
      "end": 140.69,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.69,
      "end": 141.83,
      "text": "You're adults"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.83,
      "end": 143.05,
      "text": "Can't you just get along?"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.25,
      "end": 143.59,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.59,
      "end": 144.89,
      "text": "But I fight too"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.89,
      "end": 147.55,
      "text": "So I'm guilty of the same thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.55,
      "end": 148.89,
      "text": "I'm just like"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.89,
      "end": 149.53,
      "text": "You know Abe"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.53,
      "end": 150.79,
      "text": "Abe's family too"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.79,
      "end": 152.81,
      "text": "They're fighting at every meal"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.81,
      "end": 155.35,
      "text": "They can never have a peaceful meal"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.35,
      "end": 156.97,
      "text": "And Abe is"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.97,
      "end": 157.61,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.61,
      "end": 158.51,
      "text": "As I mentioned"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.51,
      "end": 159.19,
      "text": "He's stuck"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.19,
      "end": 160.55,
      "text": "In between a rock"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.55,
      "end": 161.45,
      "text": "And a hard place"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.45,
      "end": 162.45,
      "text": "He doesn't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.45,
      "end": 163.51,
      "text": "Which side to take"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.51,
      "end": 164.03,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.03,
      "end": 166.23,
      "text": "아시다시피 우리 에이브도요"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.23,
      "end": 168.77,
      "text": "양가의 종교적인 관습에"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.77,
      "end": 170.53,
      "text": "혹은 문화적인 관습에"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.53,
      "end": 172.37,
      "text": "다 관심을 가지려고 노력을 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.37,
      "end": 174.71,
      "text": "크게 중재가 잘 안된단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.71,
      "end": 177.37,
      "text": "So he wants to be Jewish and Muslim"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.37,
      "end": 178.85,
      "text": "Which is very hard"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.85,
      "end": 180.71,
      "text": "And he starts fasting"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.71,
      "end": 183.85,
      "text": "Which many Muslims fast"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.85,
      "end": 186.17,
      "text": "And he gets in trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.17,
      "end": 186.67,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.67,
      "end": 188.03,
      "text": "Some people in his family"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.03,
      "end": 189.65,
      "text": "Do not want him to fast"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.65,
      "end": 190.07,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.07,
      "end": 192.41,
      "text": "He must have been frustrated a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.41,
      "end": 193.37,
      "text": "Very frustrated"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.37,
      "end": 195.63,
      "text": "네 일단 오늘 내용 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.63,
      "end": 198.07,
      "text": "I don't know what I'm supposed to do mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.07,
      "end": 200.01,
      "text": "There's like I don't win in either situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.01,
      "end": 202.97,
      "text": "If I do anything from the Muslim side"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.97,
      "end": 204.51,
      "text": "Then the Jewish side is going to be mad"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.51,
      "end": 206.73,
      "text": "And if I do anything from the Jewish side"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.73,
      "end": 208.17,
      "text": "Then the Muslim side is going to be mad"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.17,
      "end": 210.45,
      "text": "And if I do anything from any side"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.45,
      "end": 211.75,
      "text": "Then dad is just going to be mad"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.75,
      "end": 212.91,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.91,
      "end": 214.63,
      "text": "He's got three sides"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.63,
      "end": 215.15,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.15,
      "end": 215.91,
      "text": "The Jewish side"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.91,
      "end": 216.91,
      "text": "The Muslim side"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.91,
      "end": 217.73,
      "text": "And then dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.73,
      "end": 218.59,
      "text": "Dad's side"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.59,
      "end": 219.37,
      "text": "Dad's side"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.37,
      "end": 230.03,
      "text": "His parents had an argument last time"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.03,
      "end": 231.21,
      "text": "Another big argument"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.21,
      "end": 231.69,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.69,
      "end": 233.57,
      "text": "I think Abe heard them all"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.57,
      "end": 233.79,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.79,
      "end": 236.33,
      "text": "He heard them from his bedroom"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.33,
      "end": 237.23,
      "text": "Fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.23,
      "end": 239.09,
      "text": "And that's just a terrible feeling"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.09,
      "end": 240.23,
      "text": "For a little kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.23,
      "end": 242.51,
      "text": "To hear his parents fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.51,
      "end": 245.21,
      "text": "And he can't do anything about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.21,
      "end": 250.05,
      "text": "사실 이게 막 큰 소리 내면서 싸우는 싸움이 아니더라도"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.05,
      "end": 252.75,
      "text": "아주 작은 말다툼 소리에도"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.75,
      "end": 256.19,
      "text": "아이들은, 자녀들은 가슴이 콩닥콩닥하지 않습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.87,
      "end": 258.19,
      "text": "조금 커지기도 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.19,
      "end": 260.19,
      "text": "음성 좀 높였더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.19,
      "end": 260.91,
      "text": "아 그랬나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.03,
      "end": 262.45,
      "text": "그 정도 갖고 큰 건가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.17,
      "end": 264.67,
      "text": "It sounded pretty serious"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.67,
      "end": 264.93,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.93,
      "end": 266.99,
